@startuml
title Sơ đồ Tuần tự - Thêm Tour
actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "Browser" as UI
participant "TourAdminApiController" as Controller
participant "TourAdminService" as Service
participant "TourRepository" as Repository
database "Database" as DB

Admin -> UI: Điền thông tin Tour & Submit
activate UI
UI -> Controller: POST /api/admin/tours (TourUpsertRequest)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: create(req)
activate Service

Service -> Service: Validate Request Data (Code, Title, Category...)
Service -> Repository: save(Tour)
activate Repository
Repository -> DB: INSERT INTO tours
activate DB
DB --> Repository: Success
deactivate DB
Repository --> Service: Return saved Tour
deactivate Repository

Service --> Controller: Return TourAdminDetailResponse
deactivate Service
Controller --> UI: 200 OK (Tour Details)
deactivate Controller
UI --> Admin: Hiển thị thông báo thành công
deactivate UI

@enduml
